Pwani Oil revamps cooking oil brand. Pwani Oil Products Ltd has unveiled a new look Salit vegetable cooking oil. The new Salit is 100 per cent triple refined for total elimination of coagulation. Pwani Oil chairman Ramesh Malde said at the launch at a Mombasa hotel the revamped cooking oil targets low-income earners and will complement the firm&rsquo;s flagship Fresh Fri brand.